Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:09.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Reality slips far away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:11.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Fiction comes alive,we start to play it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:13.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hope is no more ,behind a closed door
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}As we drift away from where we were before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hope and hopelessness become one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:19.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It's all meaningless ,we've already begun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}yup, we are all one and the same
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:23.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Never opposites,we play the same game
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:25.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Walk the thin line between hope and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:26.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Running from the truth,but it's already here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Told so many lies, I dunno if they can find me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Only one life to live,so choose wisely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:32.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Heads or tails,do you even know the side you're on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:34.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Doesn't really matter if it's on the same coin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}If you wanna achieve you gotta believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:38.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It's on right now, here's the door here's the key
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:09.81,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真实离我们远去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:11.81,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在满是虚构之物的世界中 我们开始进行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:13.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望已然丢失 被遗弃在紧闭的门后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.41,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当我们离开曾经所在之处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.41,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望与绝望将合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:19.38,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}游戏已经开始 一切已无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.23,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对 我们都是命运的共同体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:23.14,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝不对立 因为我们身处同样的游戏中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:25.02,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在希望与绝望的缝隙中彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:26.88,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}逃避着真实 但它却已在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.77,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知他们是否能寻到 生活在谎言中的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.77,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有唯一的生命 必须作出聪明的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:32.52,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是否知道 自己是「黑」还是「白」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:34.40,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果相似于硬币的两面 其实也无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.20,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}渴望成功 首先要抱有信念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:38.14,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是现在 这是「门扉」 这是「钥匙」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}君の望む物は何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}耳鳴り 嘘みたいな話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:13.10,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}どうやら 僕の世界はバグってしまいました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:18.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}遮る煩悩 そいつがいうにゃ等価交換だと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:22.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}誘惑従い戯言に溺れだした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:27.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}王様ゲーム強制参加 拒否権なんて聞いちゃくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:31.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}課せられたクエストには「あの者を殺せ」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:34.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}絶望だ うっせーもう まるで少年に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:36.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}逃げ込んだ現実は ラッタッタ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:41.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欲望ないとか偽り 偽善者ぶっても仕方ねぇや
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:44.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}憧れた夢なんだっけ ヒーローになりたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:45.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}うっぷっぷ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:48.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}未来 口にする 生憎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:53.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}バカにつける薬はないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你所渴求的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.84,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那谎言般的话语 让耳鸣变得剧烈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:13.10,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}似乎我所在的世界 已经出现了程序错误
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:18.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}挡在前方的烦恼 它将其称为「等价交换」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:22.58,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在诱惑中放纵自我 沉溺于美妙的谎言中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:27.13,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}强制参加的国王游戏 否决权被彻底无视
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:31.19,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}强加于我的任务是「杀了那个人」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:34.19,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}陷入绝望了 真是烦死人啦 就如天真的少年般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:36.34,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一溜烟地 远远逃离现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:41.62,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}无欲无求只是谎言 装作伪善者也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:44.89,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是你的梦想? 渴望成为英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:45.71,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:48.67,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们谈论着未来 但很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:53.20,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}笨蛋可是无药可救的哦
